{"tid":276282,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［想呻下］新工做左就黎一個月,都係同同事熟唔到","createTime":"2017-06-08T16:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T13:21:09.000Z","uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3608032f878d40b9839e0b3bdd11de7bcf7a615","tid":276282,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟今年fg<br />\n剛剛出黎做野<br />\n一開始我見d同事有講有笑<br />\n覺得係到做野會好開心<br />\n佢地個個年資都有2年<br />\n所以佢地個個都會幫下我<br />\n但問題開始黎<br />\n我發覺工作個陣係好撚忙<br />\n係完全走唔開果隻<br />\n咁作為新仔既我當然會去問d野點做啦<br />\n頭一個星期都好地地<br />\n但之後我再問就黑我面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢地冇發脾氣但我知佢地內心一定好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋知佢地個個背後係到話我<br />\n教極都係錯,做極都係咁慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經抄底左諗著唔會錯<br />\n但有時又錯careless mistake<br />\n真係好大壓力對面佢地<br />\n大家一齊黎笑鳩我呢個垃圾又冇用fg仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba76046faabd87000334a453337b86546e67de9","tid":276282,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:40:19.000Z","msg":"唔駛介意喔，錯咪錯Lo 新人係咁ga啦，你愈介意咪愈錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4d7299da239e6517f38afaa6997057d595fefd","tid":276282,"uid":80719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"當務之急應該係諗點做好自己工作本份先，搞掂再諗人事問題，真係有野唔識唔明咪問，普遍人都係憎人懶醒多過蠢人，放膽d唔好怕柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 做邊行？"},{"pid":"c790325ac9c6a083befc0ce4332e82086823b204","tid":276282,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"屌唔做咪唔錯囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4851878300269329e5cde2760ea17339baf52b0c","tid":276282,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"